{"tid":778289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狼師揉學生乳笑稱「發育還可以」　校方竟想壓案","createTime":"2018-08-13T14:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T04:31:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bc37204da8f2081eb3e3c85847b038b6b867eebe","tid":778289,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"國一女學生遭狼師揉乳，校方竟想壓案，替狼師求情，目前仍任家教，高等法院判1年4個月。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，新竹縣１名未婚黃姓數學老師2015年9月5日上午在租屋處為1名國一女學生家教時，以她精神不濟為由，幫她摩肩頸時，雙手下滑到背及腰，少女覺得不舒服欲拒，黃男雙手搓揉她的乳房約1分鐘，還笑說「發育還可以」。<br />\n少女打給在國外出差的母親，班導師也發現她在哭，向校方反應。未料，學校卻想壓下該案，向少女母親要求簽「保密協議書」，指狼師還未滿30歲且碩士畢業，盼「給他一個機會」，少女母堅告。高等法院依「對未滿14歲女子猥褻罪」判狼師1年4個月徒刑，黃男被校方解聘，但仍任家教。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/224344_102fa32760c8f61febbcfff106ce0a60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F224344_102fa32760c8f61febbcfff106ce0a60.png&h=0b06ffea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180813/1409819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1409819&d=3GyEJJVqm9wStTpq%2FW%2B7xO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=d8576479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1409819&h=530213e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180813/1409819</a>"},{"pid":"6a59ffbc3d73d43f4de1ed630851f09d619411a9","tid":778289,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"新竹終於又一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c096b38037dc46d453ca3a9bc5c548c838d5bf2f","tid":778289,"uid":116364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf32660178be79e8387fff87c5b4124ee58444b8","tid":778289,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite